				<h3>Phase 1: Assessment and Baseline</h3>
				<ul>
					<li>Audit current AI infrastructure and costs</li>
					<li>Identify high-cost areas and optimization opportunities</li>
					<li>Establish baseline metrics and KPIs</li>
					<li>Set cost reduction targets and timelines</li>
				</ul>
				
